						               													<description>From the web-site:&amp;#10;Whether you are an aspiring Beach Bum, a wiley Business Owner, a crafty Investor or a burgeoning Divemaster this is the life for you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Along the way explore the beautiful island of Roatan, take a water taxi trip to West Bay Beach, discover the iguana farm in French Harbor, dive in and gaze upon the Roatan Marine Park, journey through the Mangroves on a secret boat ride or try your luck at Chase the Ace in West End.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whatever brings you to Roatan and wherever your adventures take you, enjoy hours of fun along the way playing The Roatan Island Game!Players choose their &amp;quot;Life Path&amp;quot; then go about the Island of Roatan in search of the Goals they need to fulfill their chosen Path and become Masters of their Life Path. Each Life Path is different so also are the Goals that make that life a success. Once you have acquired your Goals, you will be in pursuit of becoming the Governor of the Island of Roatan.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rewards and pitfalls along the way make for an exciting and challenging part of the adventure as players wind their way through the Villages of Roatan in the typical small white taxi cabs found on the Island. However, these taxi cabs are color coordinated with the &amp;quot;Life Paths&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Along the way explore the Island, take a water taxi trip to West Bay, a secret boat ride through the Mangroves or play Chase the Ace.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whatever brings you to Roatan and wherever you are going this game is sure to give you hours of fun along the way.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
